                    </div>

                    <div style="position: relative; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <div style="position: absolute; left: -1.5rem; top: 0.5rem; width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #ffc107; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid white;"></div>
                        <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #ffc107;">
                            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                                <strong>Quiz Aprobado: JavaScript Básico</strong>
                                <small style="color: #666;">10 Nov 2024</small>
                            </div>
                            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">Desarrollo Web Moderno - Calificación: 85/100</p>
